item.title: Need Help With Global Objects
item.dc:creator: @animalnt animalnt
item.description:
@animalnt wrote:

insert this into your Client.java:
make sure you have the createnewobject void

		else if (command.startsWith("object")){		
		try
		{
		int object = Integer.parseInt(command.substring(7,11));
              createNewTileObjectAll(absX, absY, object, 1, 10);
		}
		catch(Exception e) 
		{
			sendMessage("misSpelled or not an objectID"); 
		}

ok now run&Compile and test it.
::object 1533

that spawns a door
